Description: Soplos Linux Kernel Installer
 A graphical frontend for downloading, patching, compiling and installing
 the Linux kernel on Soplos Linux. Supports optimized profiles (Gaming,
 Audio/Video, Minimal, Hardware Optimized) and optional patches including
 BORE, PREEMPT_RT, Zen and NTSYNC.
 .
 Features:
  - Download kernels from kernel.org (stable, LTS, RC)
  - Patch support from official sources (BORE, PREEMPT_RT, Zen, NTSYNC)
  - Dracut initramfs generation
  - Secure Boot signing via MOK
  - NVIDIA DKMS module signing
  - 8-language interface
